Class SizedSelectingTransformer<T extends GraphElement,V>

  • java.lang.Object

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LabelFontTransformer, VertexShapeTransformer

    public abstract class SizedSelectingTransformer<T extends GraphElement,V>
extends SelectingTransformer<T,V>
    A Selecting Transformer that also tracks custom sizing information. For example, different nodes might have differently-sized shapes; fonts might be different between edges. Internally, size information is stored and calculated as Doubles.
